ScrumNinja,is,a,programming,project,management,service,that,is,designed,to,increase,efficiency,increase,productivity,and,create,greater,transparency,in,highly,complex,projects,The,ScrumNinja,API,allows,access,to,all,of,the,project,data,by,using,RESTful,calls,The,service,uses,a,secure,SSL,connection,and,is,available,on,a,tiered,pricing,scale